message: To get a high score, consistently use the 'vial' on solid ingredients first to create 'extracts' (value 30). The best combination for 100 points is often a 'magical extract' with a 'mundane extract'. If that's not possible, combining a 'magical liquid' with a 'mundane extract' yields 70 points, and then using the 'filter' on this blend will increase it to 80 points. Avoid using the 'vial' on gas or liquid ingredients, as this usually results in negative value. Aim for two 60-value items.

Avoid using the vial on liquids or gases, as it often leads to botched items with negative values.

message: To get 100 points, you need to combine a mundane liquid extract with a magical liquid (either extracted or filtered). Use the 'vial' on solid ingredients (both mundane and magical) to create 'extracted' liquids. Use the 'filter' on magical gas ingredients to create 'filtered' magical liquids. Natural magical liquids (like basilisk venom) only yield 70 points when combined, so prioritize extracting/filtering them. Always aim to create one mundane extracted liquid and one magical processed liquid, then combine them for 100 points.
